      "difficulty": 2,
      "theory": "V obchodě: Can I try this on? = Můžu si to vyzkoušet? What size? = Jaká velikost? It's too big/small. = Je to moc velké/malé. How much is it? = Kolik to stojí? I'll take it. = Vezmu si to.",
